00:22:21.490 --> 00:22:22.790
and the act of performing.

00:22:22.790 --> 00:22:27.110
That is what a dancer does
venturing into the unknown.

00:22:27.110 --> 00:22:33.040
And I was just wondering this is
maybe a good spot to talk with both

00:22:33.040 --> 00:22:36.090
of you about you each have a
troupe, you are responsible

00:22:36.090 --> 00:22:40.460
for a big aesthetic vision and
maybe something about the world

00:22:40.460 --> 00:22:43.480
of contemporary dance today
