00:27:01.170 --> 00:27:03.550
and I was thinking
back just to finish

00:27:03.550 --> 00:27:08.570 position:56%
up on your technological innovations
but I was also interested

00:27:08.570 --> 00:27:12.210 position:56%
in your comment about Graham herself
and the company have always been

00:27:12.210 --> 00:27:16.820 position:56%
on the cutting edge and you now have
a new mobile app that's downloadable

00:27:16.820 --> 00:27:19.010
if anybody is interested -

00:27:19.010 --> 00:27:20.890
&gt;&gt; Janet Eilber: And free, free -

00:27:20.890 --> 00:27:24.310
&gt;&gt; Anne McLean: What's
